    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
